news.title: Jaipur: Land record maps in shambles, all documents to go digital
news.para: JMC-Heritage commissioner Avadhesh Meena said, “We will digitise all land record maps. After the process is complete, people can access the photocopies while the originals will be kept securely to prevent further decay of paper.”

news.title: Prime minister hands over keys to 75,000 PMAY beneficiaries in Uttar Pradesh
news.para: Narendra Modi digitally handed over keys of PMAY-U houses to the beneficiaries and interacted with them.

news.title: Inspira Builders buys over two acres land in Bengaluru
news.para: The company will develop a residential township spanning over two lakh sq ft with an estimated valuation of Rs 150 crore.
